label: Digital Media
definition: A digital representation of an media object such as a Image or Sound Recording

label: Id
definition: The unique digital identifier of the object

label: Version
definition: The version of the object, each change generates a new version

label: Status
definition: The status of the Digital Object

label: Modified
definition: The timestamp that the object was last changed, which resulted in a new version of the object

label: Created
definition: The timestamp that the object was created in DiSSCo

label: Type
definition: The DOI to the FDO type of the object

label: Type
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/type

label: Access Uri
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/ac/terms/accessURI

label: Source System Id
definition: The handle to the source system object which retrieved the data from the CMS

label: Organisation Id
definition: ROR or Wikidata identifie of the organisation

label: Organisation Name
definition: Full museum name according to ROR or Wikidata

label: Format
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/format

label: License
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/license

label: Description
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/description

label: Rights
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/rights

label: Access Rights
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights

label: Rights Holder
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/rightsHolder

label: Source
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/source

label: Creator
definition: https://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator

label: Has Assertion
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Assertion objects

label: Has Citation
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Citation objects

label: Has Identifier
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Identifier objects

label: Has Entity Relationship
definition: Contains zero or more ods:EntityRelationship objects

label: Has Agent
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Agent objects

label: Tombstone Metadata
definition: Object containing the tombstone metadata of the object. Only present when ods:status is ods:Tombstone

label: Agent
definition: The Agent of the digital specimen

label: Name
definition: Full name of the agent

label: Role Name
definition: Indicates the role of the agent, https://schema.org/roleName

label: Start Date
definition: Date the agent began the role

label: End Date
definition: Date the agent ended the role

label: Role Order
definition: Order of the agent in the role. Can be used to indicate the order of importance

label: Email
definition: Email of the agent, can be present in case the agent is a maintainer of a MAS

label: Url
definition: URL of the agent, can be present in case the agent is a maintainer of a MAS

label: Has Identifier
definition: Contains zero or more ods:Identifier objects

label: Assertion
definition: The Assertion of the digital specimen

label: Measurement Id
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementID

label: Parent Measurement Id
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/parentMeasurementID

label: Measurement Type
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementType

label: Measurement Type
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/iri/measurementType

label: Measurement Determined Date
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementDeterminedDate

label: Measurement Value
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementValue

label: Measurement Value
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementValue

label: Measurement Accuracy
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementAccuracy

label: Measurement Unit
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/measurementUnit

label: Measurement Unit
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/iri/measurementUnit

label: Assertion By Agent
definition: The agent who made the assertion, contains an ods:Agent object

label: Assertion Protocol
definition: The protocol used to make the assertion

label: Assertion Protocol Id
definition: The ID of the protocol used to make the assertion

label: Assertion Remarks
definition: Remarks about the assertion

label: Citation
definition: The Citation of the digital specimen

label: Identifier
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier

label: Type
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/type

label: Date
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/date

label: Title
definition: https://purl.org/dc/terms/title

label: Creator
definition: Contains an ods:Agent object

label: Citation Page Number
definition: Page number of the citation

label: Citation Remarks
definition: Any further remarks about the citation

label: Reference Type
definition: The type of reference

label: Bibliographic Citation
definition: https://dublincore.org/usage/terms/history/#bibliographicCitation-002

label: Reference Year
definition: The year the reference was published

label: Reference Iri
definition: Reference to the web source of this citation

label: Is Peer Reviewed
definition: Is the citation peer reviewed?

label: Entity Relationship
definition: The Entity Relationship of the digital specimen

label: Relationship Of Resource
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/relationshipOfResource

label: Relationship Of Resource Id
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/relationshipOfResourceID

label: Related Resource Id
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/relatedResourceID

label: Related Resource Uri
definition: The URI of the related resource

label: Relationship Established Date
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/relationshipEstablishedDate

label: Entity Relationship Order
definition: When multiple relationships are added an order can be defined

label: Relationship According To Agent
definition: The agent who created the entity relationship. Contains an ods:Agent object

label: Relationship According To
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/relationshipAccordingTo

label: Relationship Remarks
definition: https://rs.tdwg.org/dwc/terms/relationshipRemarks
examples: ['Mother and offspring collected from the same nest']

label: Identifier
definition: The Identifier of the digital specimen

label: Title
definition: The type of the identifier, https://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title

label: Local Title
definition: The local title of the identifier

label: Identifier
definition: The value for the identifier, https://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier

label: Format
definition: Mime type of content returned by identifier in case the identifier is resolvable. https://purl.org/dc/terms/format

label: Subject
definition: Keywords qualifying the identifier https://purl.org/dc/terms/subject

label: Is Part Of Label
definition: Indicates whether the identifier is part of the physical label

label: Is Barcode Or Nfc
definition: Indicates whether the identifier is part of the barcode or nfc chip

label: Is Idpersistent
definition: Indicates whether the identifier is a persistent identifier

label: Tombstone Metadata
definition: The tombstone metadata about the tombstoned digital object

label: Tombstoned Date
definition: Timestamp the Digital Object was tombstoned and no longer active.

label: Tombstoned Text
definition: A reason why the Digital Object was tombstoned
examples: ['This is a duplicate of XXX', 'This object was made by mistake']

label: Tombstoned By Agent
definition: The agent who tombstoned the object, contains an ods:Agent object

label: Has Related Pid
definition: The PIDs of the object the tombstoned object is related to
